  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Impressive...so, what do you think? Do you want to get even stronger than you are right now? Pass a simple test and I'll do just that! Wanna do it?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Good thinking. You look strong, don't get me wrong, but there's still a need to test your strength and see if you are for real. The test isn't too difficult, so you'll do just fine...Here, take this letter first. Make sure you don't lose it."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Please get this letter to the #b#p514##k who may be around #b#m10004023##k that's near Perion. He's the one being the instructor now in place of me, as I am busy here. "
        },
        "2": {
          "_dirName": "2",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Get him the letter and he'll give you the test in place of me. For more details, hear it straight from him. Best of luck to you."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Really? It will help you out a great deal on your journey if you get stronger fast...if you choose to change your mind in the future, please feel free to come back. Know that I'll make you much more powerful than you are right now."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmmm... this is definitely the letter from #b#p511##k. So you came all the way here to take the test and make the 2nd job advancement as the warrior?"
      }
    }
